rates\", page 181.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"eastcoast-haddonfieldhadro-71\">[[#weishampel-young-1996|Weishampel and Young (1996)]]; \"Haddonfield ''Hadrosaurus''\", page 71.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cutler-4-544\">[[#tanke-2010|Tanke (2010)]]; \"Note 4,\" page 544.</ref>\n<ref name=\"cutler-9-546\">[[#tanke-2010|Tanke (2010)]]; \"Note 9,\" page 546.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"you-etal-abs-347\">[[#you-etal-2003|You et al. (2003)]]; \"Abstract\", page 347.</ref>\n<ref name=\"kobayashi-azuma-abs-166\">[[#kobayashi-azuma-2003|Kobayashi and Azuma (2003)]]; \"Abstract\", page 166.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"bolotsky-godefroit-abs-351\">[[#bolotsky-godefroit-2004|Bolotsky and Godefroit (2004)]]; \"Abstract\", page 351.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"godefroit-li-shang-abs-697\">[[#godefroit-li-shang-2005|Godefroit, Li, and Shang (2005)]]; \"Abstract\", page 697.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"prietomarquez-etal-abs-929\">[[#prietomarquez-etal-2006|Prieto-M\u00e1rquez et al. (2006)]]; \"Abstract\", page 929.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"gilpin-etal-abs-79\">[[#gilpin-dicroce-carpenter-2007|Gilpin, DiCroce and Carpenter (2007)]]; \"Abstract\", page 79.</ref>\n<ref name=\"mo-etal-abs-550\">[[#mo-etal-2007|Mo et al. (2007)]]; \"Abstract\", page 550.</ref>\n<ref name=\"zhao-etal-abs-111\">[[#zhao-etal-2007|Zhao et al. (2007)]]; \"Abstract\", page 111.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"godefroit-etal-abs-47\">[[#godefroit-etal-2008|Godefroit et al. (2008)]]; \"Abstract\", page 47.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"wagner-lehman-abs-605\">[[#wagner-lehman-2009|Wagner and Lehman (2009)]]; \"Abstract\", page 605.</ref>\n<ref name=\"peredasuperbiola-etal-abs-559\">[[#peredasuperbiola-etal-2009|Pereda-Suberbiola et al. (2009)]]; \"Abstract\", page 559.</ref>\n<ref name=\"sues-averianov-abs-2549\">[[#sues-averianov-2009|Sues and Averianov (2009)]]; \"Abstract\", page 2549.</ref>\n<ref name=\"dalla-vecchia-abs-1100\">[[#dallavecchia-2009|Dalla Vecchia (2009)]]; \"Abstract\", page 1100.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cruzadocaballero-etal-abs-1507\">[[#cruzado-caballe